        "Title": "Blood Money 2: Lights Out",
        "Location": "LOCATION_PARIS",
        "PublicId": "102187173084",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Paris/_scene_paris.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 335ce4e7-36bb-45cd-aa24-18564d48ed4e).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47.\r\r We have some business in the Sanguine Fashion Show in Paris. Ordered by Quantum Leap, they have ordered us to Eliminate our first target, &quot;The Sheikh&quot;, who has started a Technology startup that is gaining popularity, and Quantum Leap worries they will overtake them soon.\r\rCoincidentally, another client has ordered a hit on Viktor Novikov and his personal bodyguard. It has been said that Viktor is running a sex trade. Eliminate both targets to dismantle their operations.\r\r Goodluck!",
